settings.description: The universal gravitation of this ball is ALL topsy turvy! No wonder they never used this thing officially!
A remake of Super Mario World 1-2. No Yoshi here, so Goomba Shoe is used instead.
OH NO CLASSIC WATER LEVELS FROM SMB1 AAAAH,with some things of classic smb3 water levels,enjoy.
Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.
Munchers and nipper plants are alive and happily active here.

Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
A level in which Toad has broken his leg, and cant weed his lawn, and the Mario Bros. have been hired to help demolish a building due to past experience.
